entry.tran: 使非国有化;使转为私营
entry.def: To denationalize an industry or business means to transfer it into private ownership so that it is no longer owned and controlled by the state.

example.ex: The government started to denationalize financial institutions...
example.tran: 政府开始对金融机构进行私有化。
桑德兰造船厂最终转为了私营。
